textAnnotations.description:
Deadly stillness, deadly portent!
Steve awakened early and switched on
the radio, which he kept tuned to CBO
The set lighted-up but gave only a low
buzzing sound. He had just finished
shaving when it came on, with a flat
voice repeating:
"This is BBC calling
4
this is BBC calling.
